Name: UCSB
Description: A great University along the California coast!

Name: Middles (Trestles)
Description: My favorite surf break at home, were I spend most of my summers

Name: The Obervatory, Santa Ana
Description: A music venue somewhat close to where I grew up. I went to countless shows and festivals here and discovered some of my favorite artists.

Name: June Mountain
Description: The ski resort where I learned to ski and snowboard, and spent most winters of my childhood.

Name: Cracks (jalama)
Description: A break at Jalama county park where I have gotten the best waves since living here in Santa Barabara. It is relativley close but feels secluded and far away from Isla Vista.
